# Module: [network | blockchain | crypto | graphql | identity]
# Severity: [critical | high | medium | low]
# Affected Component: [QUIC | TCP | GraphQL | HSM | Blockchain | CoreBanking]
# Error Message:
# Stack Trace:
# Request ID:
# User/Session:
# Network State:
#   - QUIC connections: N
#   - TCP connections: N
#   - Pending transactions: N
# System State:
#   - CPU: N%
#   - Memory: N MB
#   - Disk I/O: N MB/s
# Action Taken:
#   - [ ] Error logged
#   - [ ] Circuit breaker triggered (if applicable)
#   - [ ] Fallback activated (if applicable)
#   - [ ] Alert sent to ops team
#   - [ ] Root cause identified

# ============================================================
# SECTION 6: Network Debug Commands (คำสั่ง Debug เครือข่าย)
# ============================================================

# Check QUIC connectivity
# quinn-diagnostics --addr 10.0.1.50:4433

# Check TCP connectivity
# nc -zv 10.0.1.50 8443

# Check mTLS handshake
# openssl s_client -connect 10.0.1.50:8443 -cert client.pem -key client-key.pem

# Check UDP port open
# nmap -sU -p 4433 10.0.1.50

# Check certificate expiry
# openssl x509 -in server.pem -noout -dates

# Check HSM slot
# pkcs11-tool --list-slots

# ============================================================
# SECTION 7: Performance Debug Commands (คำสั่ง Debug ประสิทธิภาพ)
# ============================================================

# CPU profiling (perf)
# perf record -g -p $(pgrep -f ndid-highspeed-system) -- sleep 30
# perf report

# Memory profiling (valgrind / heaptrack)
